title: Neenah Index Cardstock, 8.5" x 11", 90 lb/163 gsm, White, Lightweight, 94 Brightness, 300 Sheets (91437)
description: Create bold documents, brochures, coupons, invitations, reports, and more with Neenah White Index Cardstock. Its 90 lb. weight makes it ideal for printing in inkjet and laser printers, while each sheet is lignin and acid-free to resist yellowing and disintegration over time. The smooth texture and crisp white color reproduce high resolution images and prints for attention-getting and professional documents. Choose Neenah Paper for your next project and see for yourself!
